            . On the 20th of February last I lodged at 
               <persName id="t18090412-51-person516">
                  Edward 
                  Stanley
               <interp inst="t18090412-51-person516" type="surname" value="Stanley"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090412-51-person516" type="given" value="Edward"></interp>
